Decompose every touched spec into beads (multi-spec fan-out)

Usage: loom todo [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --since <COMMIT>    Override the anchor's `base_commit` for tier-1 detection
  -w, --workspace <PATH>  Workspace root. Defaults to the current working directory
  -A, --agent <BACKEND>   Override the agent backend for this invocation [possible values: claude, pi]
  -h, --help              Print help
